comments: Tucker (HOU) reaches in and cleanly dislodges the ball away from Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Middleton (MIL) maintains legal position contesting Westbrook's (HOU) shot near the rim.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) gathers and as he attempts to pass, Harden (HOU) deflects the ball. Antetokounmpo regathers the ball and takes two legal steps prior to passing.
Tucker (HOU) makes marginal contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) back as he is defending the pass.
Covington (HOU) makes contact to Middleton's (MIL) wrist during his shooting motion and the contact affect his jump shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) slightly extends his arm against Matthews' (MIL) and disengages.
Matthews (MIL) makes clean contact with the ball during Harden's (HOU) drive and maintains a legal guarding position.
Tucker (HOU) makes incidental contact to Matthews' (MIL) body after the release of his jump shot attempt and does not affect his ability to follow through.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact to Lopez's (MIL) body on his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with Westbrook's (HOU) arm during his upward shooting motion.
Covington (HOU) legally contest Antetokounmpo's (MIL) driving shot attempt and absorbs the contact.
Harden (HOU) makes some contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body during the pick and disengages.

Antetounkoumpo (MIL) touches the rim without shaking it or moving it off center. The contact with the rim by Antetounkoumpo was not made while the ball was on the rim or in the cylinder nor did it make the ball take an unnatural bounce.
Middleton (MIL) makes contact to Westbrook's (HOU) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) beats Antetokounmpo (MIL) to the spot and absorbs the contact as Antetokounmpo redirects his path.
Korver (MIL) makes contact with House Jr.'s (HOU) arm affecting his pass attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm after gathering the loose ball.
Covington (HOU) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Middleton (MIL) following the release of his shot as he extends his foot in an outward motion.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) wraps Harden (HOU) affecting his FOM.
